---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: "Greinar"
description: "[TBD — íslensk lýsing] Greinar um brunaþéttingar, brunavarnir og skráningar fyrir mannvirki á Íslandi."
permalink: /greinar/
eleventyNavigation:
  key: articles-is
  order: 6
  parent: false
---
{%- set featured = articles | selectattr("featured") | first %}
{%- set rest = articles | rejectattr("featured") %}

<section class="page-hero">
  <img class="page-hero__image" src="/img/documentation.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="900">
  <div class="scrim"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="crumbs"><a href="/">Heim</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; <span>Greinar</span></div>
    <h1>Greinar og leiðbeiningar.</h1>
    <p class="kicker">[TBD — íslenska] Hagnýt ráð frá brunaþéttingateymi okkar.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="articles">
  <div class="container">
    {%- if featured %}
    <a class="article-featured" href="/greinar/{{ featured.slug }}/">
      <div class="pic">
        <img src="{{ featured.image }}" alt="" width="1200" height="900">
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="tag">{{ featured.category[lang] }}</div>
        <h2>{{ featured.title[lang] }}</h2>
        <p>{{ featured.summary[lang] }}</p>
        <div class="meta">
          <span>{{ featured.date | dateDisplay(lang) }}</span>
          <span><strong>{{ featured.readTimeMinutes }} mín</strong> lestur</span>
          <span>{{ featured.author }}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
    {%- endif %}

    <div class="article-grid">
      {%- for article in rest %}
      <a class="article-card" href="/greinar/{{ article.slug }}/">
        <div class="pic">
          <img src="{{ article.image }}" alt="" width="1200" height="900">
          <span class="tag">{{ article.category[lang] }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
          <h3>{{ article.title[lang] }}</h3>
          <p>{{ article.summary[lang] }}</p>
          <div class="meta">
            <span>{{ article.date | dateDisplay(lang) }}</span>
            <span>{{ article.readTimeMinutes }} mín</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <h2>Tilbúin að hefja verkefnið? <span class="ul">Hafðu samband.</span></h2>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn primary" href="/verdreiknir/"><span>Fá verðmat</span> <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="#contact"><span>Senda fyrirspurn</span> <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
